Cell["\<\
Plotting all the data trajectories. Younger ones seem to asymptote right \
away, suggesting overdamped behavior ( < 96.1 hrs). Older ones start \
oscillating a little bit. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.978098732763857*^9, 3.9780987547014437`*^9}, {
